text: Kenneth Magidson (born April 4, 1948) is an American attorney who served as the United States Attorney for the Southern District of Texas from 2011 to 2017. ==See also== *2017 dismissal of U.S. attorneys ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:United States Attorneys for the Southern District of Texas Category:Texas Democrats Category:Assistant United States Attorneys Category:University System of Maryland alumni Category:South Texas College of Law alumni Category:20th-century American lawyers Category:21st-century American lawyers
